Gennis.  I wrote it while I was a graduate  student in   Physics at UC
Santa Cruz, and was also working as a programmer.     I was manic when I
wrote this - I meant to write just a brief note and ended up writing for
twelve hours.  During this manic episode I was experiencing peculiar
irregularities and disclocations in time and space.  My experience of
the time I spent writing this was that perhaps an hour had passed.  As I
wrote, I made cup after cup of tea - it seemed to me that when I put the
